div.div:
UART TX Feed FSM
This FSM feeds the TX FIFO of the uart_tx_only module.
The data to feed to the TX FIFO is always a 34 8-bit character line of ASCII text.
The tx_go input is triggered by the corresponding wr_clear_display pulse on the
Pmod CLS custom driver, such that the UART TX Feed occurs when the LCD is
starting to update on the FSM cycle of that driver.
